title: War of the Roses: He Won't Let Her Come to Doggie Classes
description: Jackie went pretty far to make sure her boyfriend was behaving, all the way to New Orleans, and caught him with girls on his lap at a pool.  Now they have a dog and he won't let her come to doggie classes and she doesn't understand why.  Is he bringing someone else with him or what?
